---
title: "SSD UC6 — Chat with Story Character"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as ":User"
    participant S as ":System"

    Note over User,S: System treated as BLACK BOX<br/>UC6 — Chat with Story Character

    User->>S: openCharacterChat(storyId)
    S-->>User: characterList(characters[])

    User->>S: selectCharacter(storyId, characterName)
    S-->>User: chatSessionReady(character, greeting)

    loop multi-turn conversation
        User->>S: sendMessage(storyId, characterName, userMessage)
        S-->>User: characterResponse(response, character)
    end

    User->>S: closeChat()
    S-->>User: chatClosed
